					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-4099042#post-3624167</guid>
				<title>Re: Creating a Hub</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-4099042/kit-s-horror-hospital-of-horror#post-3624167</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2017 16:50:08 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Decibelles</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2005044</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>You have four tales, so you're already past the requirement for making a hub.</p> <p>The only rules for a hub are that you link to your tales on it really! It can look however you want; I'd look at all the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/series-archive">different series</a> on here to see if you wanna model it after anything. And it helps by giving your tale series more exposure, even if just in the moment you post the hub!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
