				<wikidot:authorName>Kakroom</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2198340</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Very nice horrorshow stuff. I didn't go to the crosslink, because I don't do that, but you managed the modt important aspect of, that, aspect - that is, the article works and articulates the ancillary subject's abilities without relyin on thr merit of the aforementioned subject's main dossier. And the psychiatric hospital stuff is good too; the way you characterized the dull hostility of it all harkened back to Terry Gilliam's 12 Monkeys a little, and even without Brad Pitt's batshittery that made the juxtaposition with Kit's friend very eerie in hindsight.</p> <p>+1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
